/*２２２２２２２２２２２２２２ 測試中：亮黃底色  ❦✈♕❄❤❦✪⁂☽❧❣☯❂✯☪☸ꕥ */
 embed, label [onclick],  div[style*="-moz-user-select"],   span[class*="script"] div,  ul[style*="visibility:"] ul, a[id*="ghosteryfirefox"], #ghostery-purple-bubble, #translator-popup, .hovercard, .vbmenu_popup 
